This repository is made publicly viewable to support academic peer review,
research reproducibility, and non-commercial evaluation of the associated
paper, "Stall-Free Software--Hardware Co-Design for Perception-Driven CLAHE".

1. Permitted Use

You may download, inspect, run, and modify the code, scripts, configuration
files, representative RTL, and derived result files in this repository for
non-commercial academic research, teaching, peer review, and reproducibility
evaluation.

2. Attribution Requirement

Any use of this repository, its code, RTL, scripts, results, figures, or
derivative implementations in a publication, thesis, report, presentation,
repository, benchmark, or product documentation must clearly cite the associated
paper and this repository. You must preserve copyright notices, this license,
and citation metadata.

3. Prohibited Conduct

You may not:

- present this repository, its unpublished research results, or derivative work
  based on it as your own original work;
- remove citation, copyright, or license notices;
- use the repository for commercial products, services, sublicensing, paid
  consulting deliverables, or proprietary benchmarks without written permission
