- redistribute source datasets, raw videos, third-party media, or other material
  not included in this repository;
- use the repository in a way that violates the license terms of any third-party
  dataset, model, library, FPGA IP, or media source.

4. Redistribution

You may share links to the original repository. Redistribution of modified
copies is allowed only for non-commercial academic purposes and only if the
modified copy preserves this license, the citation metadata, and a clear notice
